Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:56.67,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}巻き戻せない物語
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:21:02.53,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}答えばかり求める心が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:08.49,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}理由のいらない喜びに震えた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.79,0:21:13.41,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}初めて思いが通じ合ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:19.59,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}この夢が　この愛が　どんなに刹那でもかまわない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:20.22,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}残らず
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:22.72,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:26.00,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}My Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:30.56,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}幸せをくれた人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:34.31,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}かけがえのない希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:38.49,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}醒めては　また彷徨う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.32,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}夢の中で　ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:45.91,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}ずっとあなたを探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.91,0:21:49.16,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}何度も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:53.38,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}覚えた甘い痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:57.00,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}ひとつだって忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:22:02.72,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}繋ぐ指　約束は　解けないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:05.01,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}あなたの夢が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:07.92,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}ちゃんと叶うように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:12.00,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}歌うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:25.41,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}大切に思うたび強く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.91,0:22:31.20,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}運命が胸を締め付ける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:07.27,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}失ってもあなたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.27,0:23:10.92,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}夢も　全部守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:13.79,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}愛しくて　愛しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.79,0:23:16.17,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}伝えきれないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:18.79,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}ただまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:21.55,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}信じあえたこと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:53.63,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}もう一度だけ　歌えるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.77,0:24:02.17,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&}また　あなたのために
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.43,0:20:14.23,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}如光束般相连的旋律
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.79,0:20:20.20,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}如今为你跃动
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.20,0:20:39.59,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}在邂逅之时
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.88,0:20:46.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}我们之间的一切就已有定局
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.66,0:20:51.35,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}在雨后晴空之下 我不再迷茫
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.35,0:20:56.67,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}过往不再可追
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.30,0:21:02.53,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}一心求索的心灵
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.94,0:21:08.49,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}为不需理由的喜悦而感动
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.79,0:21:13.41,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}我们第一次心意相通
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.61,0:21:19.59,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}即使这场梦 这份爱仅有一瞬的须臾
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.59,0:21:20.22,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}不顾一切
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.22,0:21:22.72,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}紧紧拥抱你
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.99,0:21:26.00,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}我亲爱的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.18,0:21:30.56,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}给予我幸福
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.56,0:21:34.31,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}和独一无二的希望
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.31,0:21:38.49,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}梦醒之后 再度徘徊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.32,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}梦境之中 一直
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.99,0:21:45.91,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}一直寻找着你
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.91,0:21:49.16,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fax-0.1\blur3\3c&H7CB6C6&\fs55}多少次
